intro: Train your mind, enjoy the process and discover new facets of pleasure in the world of Sudoku!
description:
Welcome to Doku Girls 3 – an exciting puzzle game that will help you develop your logic and attentiveness! For successfully completing levels, you will receive a special reward – charming images of beautiful girls. Immerse yourself in a relaxing atmosphere thanks to pleasant music and bright graphics.

Game features:
• Images of girls that are unlocked as you progress
• Unique, hand-made sudoku for any skill level
• Sensual music that creates an atmosphere of relaxation and pleasure
